==English==
===Pronunciation===
*kŏl'əm, /ˈkɒləm/, /<tt>"kQl@m</tt>/
*:[[Rhymes:English:-ɒləm|Rhymes: -ɒləm]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# An upright supporting [[beam]].
# A vertical line of entries in a [[table]], going from [[top]] to [[bottom]]; as opposed to a [[horizontal]] [[row]] (going from [[left]] to [[right]]).
# Anything having similar form or structure to 1. or 2., such as a column of troops, a newspaper column, spinal column, etc.

====Antonyms====
*[[row]]

